270,"  Ashoka University: Leading Liberal Arts and Sciences University                                                                                                                                                                                Search for:                                                                      Other links:  Other links:         Music and Cognition is a survey course that will introduce students to key questions across topics of research interest in the field, including music and evolution, music and development, music and emotion, music and nonmusical cognitive abilities, performing and composing music, and listening to and liking music. The assessments will be a combination of MCQ tests taken over different points in the term and a collaborative project  where students will generate podcasts in small groups that they will receive ongoing feedback on.                      Programme Interested InUndergraduate ProgrammeYoung India FellowshipYSPPhDMA - EconomicsMA EnglishMSC Biology Year of Admission2022-232023-242024-252025-26  Subscribe to our communications [current_url]     Plot No. 2, Rajiv Gandhi Education City, National Capital Region P.O. Rai, Sonepat         Haryana-131029 (India)  Ashoka University Plot no.222, Second floor, Okhla Industrial Estate, Phase III, New Delhi-110020        Email Address*                  Copyright © Ashoka University: Leading Liberal Arts and Sciences University              ",852c3dfd-05d5-4be4-8ca8-7f8bf58890b1
